Installation of Night-Vision Application

1. Install new Raspberry Pi OS Image

2. git Installation
$ sudo apt upgrade
$ sudo apt install git
$ git config --global user.name "retomarti"
$ git config --global user.email "retomarti@me.com"

3. Clone github Repository
$ git clone https://github.com/retomarti/voxatec-night-vision.git
$ git checkout main

4. Enable Pi-Camera
$ sudo raspi-config
  -> Enable legacy camera module
  
5. Install OpenCV
https://medium.com/codemonday/opencv4-python3-raspberry-pi-installation-guide-9182ed893ae6
https://www.jeremymorgan.com/tutorials/raspberry-pi/how-to-install-opencv-raspberry-pi/

5. Run Web-Application
$ cd <appl-directory>
$ python3 night-vision.py

6. See Night-Vision Stream from Camera
Get ip-Address
$ ip a   -> under wlan' -> inet <ip-address>
Enter URL in browser: 
- local: http://127.0.0.1:5000/
- remote: http://<ip-address>:5000/


https://python.hotexamples.com/examples/picamera/PiCamera/capture_continuous/python-picamera-capture_continuous-method-examples.html
